@startuml
title Детектирование threshold event

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> ReadPercent

ReadPercent : вычислить selected interval
ReadPercent --> WaitingForSamples : percentage is NaN
WaitingForSamples --> ReadPercent : следующий collection

ReadPercent --> BelowThreshold : rounded percent < threshold
BelowThreshold --> ReadPercent : следующий collection

ReadPercent --> Cooldown : now < event floor
Cooldown --> ReadPercent : floor expired

ReadPercent --> EventRecorded : percent >= threshold\nи floor expired
EventRecorded : увеличить psistat_event_total
EventRecorded : сохранить timestamp и percent
EventRecorded : установить floor = now + interval
EventRecorded --> ReadPercent : следующий collection

@enduml
